title: Radha Govinda
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Indian, Buffet, Salad bar, Take-out
description: Hare Krishna affiliated restaurant, previously known as Govinda's. The daily hot food offering include a vegan dish, a vegetarian dish, an Indian dish, a Mediterranean dish, soup, rice/potatoes/couscous, and 2 kinds of more exotic food. There is an additional salad bar and desserts bar. Closed through mid-August.
